 <p>Additionally, for the entire duration of <a href="#individual">Individual's</a> participation in the
  WHATWG, such <a href="#individual">Individual</a> hereby agrees that they will, as soon as is
  reasonably practicable:</p>

 <ul>
   <li>identify and disclose any patent or patent application of which they are personally aware that
     they believe contains claims that are or may become Essential Patent Claims for any
     <a href="https://whatwg.org/workstream-policy#workstream">Workstream</a> in which they are
     participating; and
   </li>
   <li>notify the <a href="https://whatwg.org/sg-agreement#steering-group">Steering Group</a> of any
     (1) change in employment or affiliation; and (2) possible conflicts of interest, including, without
     limitation, conflicts relating to participation in other standards organizations or involvement in
     other projects that might compete with the work of the
     <a href="https://whatwg.org/workstream-policy#workstream">Workstream</a> in which such
     <a href="#individual">Individual</a> is participating.
   </li>
 </ul>

 <p>Each <a href="#individual">Individual</a> hereby represents and warrants that such
   <a href="#individual">Individual</a> has all rights necessary in and to any
   <a href="https://whatwg.org/ipr-policy#21-contribution">Contributions</a> it makes during the course
   of such <a href="#individual">Individual's</a> participation, and that making
   <a href="https://whatwg.org/ipr-policy#21-contribution">Contributions</a> or executing this Agreement
   will not violate, conflict with, or result in the breach of any other agreement with or obligation to
   any other party.
 </p>

